Usage:

Add or replace parameter:

    -Override /SwitchWithValue:'SomeValue'

    -Override /Switch

Remove parameter:

    -Override -/Switch

Multiple overrides:

    -Override `"/ReplaceThisSwitchWithValue:'SomeValue' -/RemoveThisSwitch /AddThisSwitch`"
"
        )]
